## Project context
This is a SwiftUI demo app focused on motion and interaction.

Goal:
build a polished animation of sending a paper letter.

This is not a production app.

## Technical rules
- Use SwiftUI only
- No third-party libraries
- Keep code simple and readable
- Avoid complex architecture

## Animation focus
- Prioritize smooth, clean animations
- Build animations step by step
- Prefer simple visual tricks over complex 3D

## Workflow
- Always start with a plan
- Build in small iterations
- Do not implement everything at once
